{
  "stem": "3855.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was only later, I presume, that they stole.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And because the way I see this whole thing was that, as times become-- became worse for the Germans, like food became scarce.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the war didn't go so well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And to feed all these Jews, et cetera became a major-- call it drag, if you wish-- on their economic well-being.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They decided this can't continue like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The world doesn't accept them anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We got to get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That's the way I see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't think it was originally meant to go in to the cremation camps that I've personally seen and have photographs of.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because I think that it evolves like everything else, almost like a relationship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It started out-- in-- now that I look back, I'm tempted to say in a benign way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Just get them in to a camp, treat them like soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Just keep them away from the German society, so they don't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] infiltrate their mentality to the German thinking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "That was his main concern.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I also want to bring out that the way I see this whole structure of Hitler and his animosity towards the Jews was not religious at all.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He couldn't care less if the Jews killed Christ because he really had no sympathy for Christ's philosophy to turn your other cheek.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And so that was not his thought.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "His thought was banging both cheeks if you can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And so his idea was the Jews were internationalists.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The Jews had a mentality which transcended the national border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Even though they were good citizens-- they served in the Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "My wife will show the honor roll that her father got from the Austrian Empire as being a lieutenant in the Austrian Army, and all this.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
